                "2017a",
                ")",
                " enables clients to collaboratively train machine learning models without sharing their local data with other parties. Due to its privacy-preserving nature, FL has attracted considerable attention across various domains in real-world applicationsÂ ",
                "(Hard etÂ al., ",
                "2018",
                "; Chen etÂ al., ",
